s=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係問下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為文學歷史乜q都好勁"},{"pid":"247a85b8c11672d93faffac562c34b1ee6844f4d","tid":203384,"uid":46366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實有冇人諗過本野唔只係金庸一個人作？</blockquote><br />\n講緊倪匡寫嗰part?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n倪匡有份寫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b867d4d2af4a13cb479491948349855a00904db4","tid":203384,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:03:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有冇人諗過本野唔只係金庸一個人作？</blockquote><br />\n老老實實<br />\n我覺得遊坦之同阿紫相遇去到阿紫盲撚左<br />\n都唔係金庸寫<br />\n<br />\n紫盲就講到明係倪匡寫啦<br />\n金庸都話係得盲呢一part先係倪匡寫 其他倪寫既都刪哂<br />\n<br />\n但我又覺得戴面具同啜腳金庸寫唔出"},{"pid":"1acb24c925f21c9cf88804e6fd30bf52c407c883","tid":203384,"uid":64227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實有冇人諗過本野唔只係金庸一個人作？</blockquote><br />\n講緊倪匡寫嗰part?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n倪匡有份寫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似係金庸唔得閒搵咗倪匡代筆一排，倪匡好憎阿紫所以寫盲咗佢，之後金庸寫返又醫返好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a520d0c8b335930c3987dfe4e96233a532049e","tid":203384,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:04:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實有冇人諗過本野唔只係金庸一個人作？</blockquote><br />\n講緊倪匡寫嗰part?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n倪匡有份寫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阿紫盲果part係佢寫<br />\n其實佢寫左好多<br />\n因為連載時金庸去左旅行無得停稿<br />\n<br />\n但金庸話出書已經刪哂倪寫既部分<br />\n但盲佢覺得有意思就keep低"},{"pid":"8d0c586fb854ed8465da8ea725d06666f37ed82e","tid":203384,"uid":1399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:08:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實有冇人諗過本野唔只係金庸一個人作？</blockquote><br />\n講緊倪匡寫嗰part?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n倪匡有份寫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阿紫盲果part係佢寫<br />\n其實佢寫左好多<br />\n因為連載時金庸去左旅行無得停稿<br />\n<br />\n但金庸話出書已經刪哂倪寫既部分<br />\n但盲佢覺得有意思就keep低</blockquote><br />\n我諗唔止咁少啦"},{"pid":"a29ac7a7a2c35099b032dc425a808b8614d513c1","tid":203384,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img2.artfoxlive.com/uploadFile/productImg/201608/l/1470828770263_294081_origin.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg2.artfoxlive.com%2FuploadFile%2FproductImg%2F201608%2Fl%2F1470828770263_294081_origin.jpg&h=4ffd344c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n書入面有個大遼面具張相<br />\n<br />\n真係睇到心都寒鳩埋"},{"pid":"d7763a1109f23300e96e2722a2e108c2152cbd01","tid":203384,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:40:48.000Z","msg":"唔太記得劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但天龍真係睇得最爽最fantasy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27058088afd935e327ec85e7838aab50c7cd3e66","tid":203384,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:51:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔太記得劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但天龍真係睇得最爽最fantasy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中學同學都話悶<br />\n但我覺得好正"},{"pid":"833a0c0e56defe2834f5aa67af5793dce254e012","tid":203384,"uid":89868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T18:07:17.000Z","msg":"其實點解咁多連登仔都係到話  天龍三主角結局都sad呢<br />\n<br />\n蕭峰就話係慘姐    但虛竹對死左老豆老母睇化左  一直以黎都係對做唔返和尚而耿耿於懷    而係結尾段譽都成功開解左佢  話出家同唔出家冇分別  唔出家都可以拜佛同推行佛法<br />\n段譽方面  最後佢雖然同唔到王語嫣一齊  但佢明白到自己一直咁痴戀王係源於心魔  最後佢心魔已解  佢都冇覺得留戀  反而係開心wo  所謂各有各的緣法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}